### Booking statuses:
# - PENDING: Initial booking state
# - CONFIRMED: Booking confirmed by admin/agent
# - ACTIVE: Booking is currently active
# - COMPLETED: Booking has been completed
# - CANCELLED: Booking has been cancelled 